Class SwitchInfo

java.lang.Object
redecker.mickey.webcnc.types.SwitchInfo
public class SwitchInfo extends Object
This class represents the information required to gather TSN and LLDP data from the switch via SNMPv3

  • Constructor Details

    • SwitchInfo

      public SwitchInfo(String switchIdentifier, String address, Integer port, String authUserName, String authAlgorithm, String authPassword, String encryptAlgorithm, String encryptPassword, String tsnPortsString)
      Parameters:
      switchIdentifier - a unique identifier
      address - the IP address of the switch
      port - The SNMP-UDP port of the switch
      authUserName - the SNMPv3 authentication user name
      authAlgorithm - the SNMPv3 authentication algorithm
      authPassword - the SNMPv3 authentication password
      encryptAlgorithm - the SNMPv3 encryption Algorithm
      encryptPassword - the SNMPv3 encryption password
      tsnPortsString - a String indicating the TSN-capable ports on the switch
